<h3 id=3D"id-07.SD:AccountGrouping-Non-FunctionalRequirementsTraceability">=
Non-Functional Requirements Traceability</h3>
<p><a href=3D"/display/ARTC/Non-Functional+Requirements">Non-Functional Req=
uirements</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<h1 id=3D"id-07.SD:AccountGrouping-Solution"><span>Solution</span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"id-07.SD:AccountGrouping-SolutionOverview"><span>Solution Overvie=
w</span></h2>
<p><span>The solution talks about how to fetch and list the account listing=
 for both closed and active accounts.</span></p>
<p>In the Galaxy Accounts MFE we will introduce a change in the existing en=
dpoint and one new endpoint:</p>
<ol>
<li>To fetch a account groups - GET- (/accountGroups)</li>
<li>Addition of query param(ScopeId i.e. group id) in existing endpoint GET=
 /arrangements to fetch the account listing associated with the group selec=
ted.</li>
</ol>
