<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(23,43,77);">Accounts MFE</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>PDP Server Side l=
ibrary</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol>
<li>To fetch a account groups - GET- (/accountGroups)</li>
<li>Addition of query param(ScopeId i.e. group id) in existing endpoint GET=
 /arrangements to fetch the account listing associated with the group selec=
ted.</li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
